<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />How great is your goodness</para>

<para style="q1">that you have stored up for those who revere you,</para>

<para style="q1">that you perform for those who take refuge in you</para>

<para style="q1">before all the children of mankind!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />In the shelter of your presence, you hide them from the plots of men.</para>

<para style="q1">You hide them in a shelter from the violence of tongues.</para>
